{"tid":2059432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：教育局反對罷課　教師事假僅可用於紅白二事","createTime":"2020-06-11T02:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T02:59:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"392f33573ebd0ef943517e0fce0e63aa4380f48b","tid":2059432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄在一個電台節目表示，教育局反對政治帶入校園，以及反對任何形式罷課的態度基本上無改變，強調作為專業教師，不應該罷課。他又指，參與罷課並非教師申請事假的原因，當局只是重申一貫立場，教師只可以用事假處理紅白二事等緊急事務。<br />\n<br />\n教聯會副主席鄧飛則表示，教育局去信學校反對有組織罷課的力度及立場變得更鮮明及明確，認為教育局反對罷課無可厚非，否則教育體系會崩潰。被問到如果有人在校外築成人鏈，校方會否阻止，鄧飛說，如果有關範圍不屬於校方，學校就管不到，但如果阻礙學生上課，就當然要管。"},{"pid":"5e58d8f8ee54064a5e0a5bdc6d0ff81d9e0d4366","tid":2059432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305930&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1305930%26csid%3D261_341&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=5d01da73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305930&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e50ee23c4366664f52d288eb52d65c0c97966116","tid":2059432,"uid":37876,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ead327e186e405d736d88b69a9d3ce84481d56","tid":2059432,"uid":92064,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:17:49.000Z","msg":"唔好比人病呀笨"},{"pid":"a065559719f5f5d51673ab48a68b529727adefea","tid":2059432,"uid":74361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"去飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/